<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-2481] Adding large TYPE_BYTE_BINARY image to pdf document generates distorted result</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2481</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;See attached &lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12679185/12679185_small.jpg&quot; title=&quot;small.jpg attached to PDFBOX-2481&quot;&gt;small.jpg&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; and &lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12679186/12679186_large.jpg&quot; title=&quot;large.jpg attached to PDFBOX-2481&quot;&gt;large.jpg&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; added to attached &lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12679184/12679184_rgb.pdf&quot; title=&quot;rgb.pdf attached to PDFBOX-2481&quot;&gt;rgb.pdf&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; and &lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12679183/12679183_bn.pdf&quot; title=&quot;bn.pdf attached to PDFBOX-2481&quot;&gt;bn.pdf&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; using attached &lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12679187/12679187_Image2Pdf2ImageBlackAndWhite2PDF.java&quot; title=&quot;Image2Pdf2ImageBlackAndWhite2PDF.java attached to PDFBOX-2481&quot;&gt;Image2Pdf2ImageBlackAndWhite2PDF.java&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Adding both small.jpg and large.jpg to rgb.pdf is OK&lt;br/&gt;
Adding small.jpg, converted to black and white, to bn.pdf is OK&lt;br/&gt;
Adding large.jpg, converted to black and white, to bn.pdf is NOK: the resulting image is distorted.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
